cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM

The paper deals with image synthesis from semantic layouts, which is a problem in computer vision. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also uses deep learning techniques, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves constructing a memory bank of image segments, which could be related to cs.GR (Graphics) or cs.MM (Multimedia).
